                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420228-1099-offence-1 t18420228-name-1327"></join>Michael Meyers</persName>, in his dwelling-house: and 12 shillings, the monies of <persName id="t18420228-name-1328" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1328" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1328" type="surname" value="BANBURY"></interp>
